		PRODUCTION MANAGEMENT - USER MANUAL

Before of all below step, we need to build excel lib. Go to ProductionManagement/package/libxlsxwriter directory then type
	make 

Then we run autoconf by shell script autogen.sh with command:
	./autogen.sh


[BUILD]: Only build and install PM into 'dir' directory. 

	./build_pm -d <dir> -m -su

"-d" is optical. Defauft install directory is /usr/local


[PACKAGE]: Create a 'ProductionManagement.deb' install file. That will be install on other Debian/Ubuntu.

	./build_pm -p -pkg_name ProductionManagement -r -su

"-r" 			option will remove all debug information from source code on terminal.
"-pkg_name"  <a>	'a' can change to other leter or empty


************************************************************************************************************

To use Courier font:
	apt-get install ttf-mscorefonts-installer

To use alsa driver to play alert sound
	apt-get install alsa-utils

mpg321 -w alert.wav alert.mp3
